      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c15efcdeda6b3608575c0af"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "I would expect no less than the wrath of the 'Dragon' for attempting to interfere on their success, if I had tried to replicate the <i>Polymer Coated Man</i> in a world close to Kurita space.\n\nMy mistake was expecting that I could avoid their ISF spies by moving to the other side of the galaxy.",
      "branches": [
